{"tid":892182,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"要分辨條女質地係咪靚，最緊要睇佢老母","createTime":"2018-11-06T16:38:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-06T17:07:36.000Z","uid":5584,"like":7,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"cc3e8f944a5e6ebbfcfa256347fa0ed6a43c53b4","tid":892182,"uid":5584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T16:38:51.000Z","msg":"老實說，要分辨一個女仔靚唔靚<br />\n最緊要係睇佢老母<br />\n如果佢老母如果仲係果種風韻猶存，成個周慧敏咁<br />\n即係條女十年後如無意外都仲係靚女<br />\n如果佢老母個樣同身型成個Maria Corderoo 咁<br />\n就算佢個女幾靚，你都應該要鳩縮<br />\n因為佢大個左就會變成咁<br />\n<br />\n當然你會同我講我係現在屌佢，唔係同佢做人世<br />\n但你諗下如果你有一日午夜夢迴<br />\n你諗返起你曾經屌過舊豬肉<br />\n到時我真係要恭喜你呀<br />\n<br />\n所以一句講哂，要分辨條女個質地靚唔靚<br />\n最緊要睇佢老母"},{"pid":"6f21c757cc4329b68729e9ed753b23e0673b3b46","tid":892182,"uid":5584,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T16:46:15.000Z","msg":"利申：<br />\n<br />\n試過上個女仔屋企，屌緊條女<br />\n突然見到佢老母張相成個杜特爾突咁<br />\n<br />\n要即時休返條褲"},{"pid":"a33500e3378b2632f8415fb797be6b5758bfc3ec","tid":892182,"uid":180948,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T16:52:09.000Z","msg":"女多數似老豆<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3e4768e61cd6ea8d1dbaf6475e9f0cabb1410ea","tid":892182,"uid":86756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T16:57:28.000Z","msg":"Angel baby 個case點計"},{"pid":"1aede820255a3752ff521b3e244a095b1839d7a8","tid":892182,"uid":19005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T16:57:55.000Z","msg":"屌你老母"},{"pid":"7a24c29fad9c42ef97de2d8fea3e558b93a62831","tid":892182,"uid":121409,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T17:00:54.000Z","msg":"睇條女係咪靚，最緊要竟然唔係睇條女，係睇佢老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6fa9d165df1fa987b4a62e91dbca1cb5b2d40045","tid":892182,"uid":29929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7a24c29fad9c42ef97de2d8fea3e558b93a62831","